Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.42,0:23:41.79,op-jp,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}世界を拡げよう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.79,0:23:43.80,op-cn,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.51,0:22:17.24,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}早安 世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.24,0:22:20.31,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fsp0}Good Morning World!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.47,0:22:33.98,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我脚步不停
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.98,0:22:37.94,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只有双脚的痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.94,0:22:41.03,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}知晓走过的距离
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.48,0:22:48.12,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我期待着漫漫长夜后的绝美风景
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.12,0:22:51.14,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}活在今天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.16,0:22:57.21,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}神之灵峰 新绿宫殿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.21,0:23:02.26,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}岩窟深处 苍穹尽头
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.26,0:23:08.05,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}都要一一到达 永无止境
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.05,0:23:11.20,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我要走遍每一个角落
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.99,0:23:15.02,op-cn,,0,0,2,,{\blur2}早安 世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.02,0:23:18.27,op-cn,,0,0,2,,{\blur2\fsp0}Good Morning World!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.27,0:23:22.07,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}驱散名为不可能的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.07,0:23:27.66,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}将神话变为日常的{\fsp0}Odyssey
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.11,0:23:36.87,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}一步又一步 如滴水穿石般
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.42,0:23:41.79,op-cn,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}拓宽眼前的世界
